## DESCRIPTION
## Gear between two moving racks, determine angular vel., ICZV location, vel. at centre
## ENDDESCRIPTION

## KEYWORDS('gear','rack','relative motion','velocity','angular velocity','acceleration','angular acceleration')
## DBsubject(Dynamics)
